snippet.title: Megadeth - "Hangar 18" | Haider Ali (Guitar Cover) #Shorts
snippet.description:
“Hangar 18” by @Megadeth from the album Rust in Peace — released in 1990 under @Capitol Records, and produced by Mike Clink at Rumbo Recorders in Los Angeles, CA, USA 
— guitar performance by @Haider Ali.

• Subscribe
https://www.youtube.com/haidertonight?sub_confirmation=1

• Thoughts
Hey, folks! A lot of you may agree that Hangar 18 is one of the best, if not 'the best,' Megadeth song, and I like this one because of its' fast-paced nature and the sheer tone of pure brutality — it is a banger for sure. I hope you guys find this short version interesting. Cheers!
